    <briefdescription>
<para>Resource representing the physical and logical geometry settings of the display panel. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Exposes logical panel dimensions (pixels/points) and physical dimensions (millimeters), and computes the derived DPI ratio (pixels per inch) dynamically. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
